Text:
Thank you to whomever does these....!

Wondering if those with these shows could help others of us out.....

I need just a few meg to finish 2010.02.12 and 2010.03.10, and I know others and I are still waiting for actual seeding of 2010.04.02, 2010.04.01, 2010.03.30, 2010.03.29.  If you have these and can put them up for a day or so, I'd really appreciate it and would seed them for a few days from there such that all of us who've been looking for them on and off would be taken care of.  Would also love 2009.12.24.

Thanks!
